1383:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         LL_ADC_CHANNEL_TEMPSENSOR, ...),
1384:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC external channel (LL_ADC_CHANNEL_1, LL_ADC_CHANNEL_2, ...),
1385:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         must not be a value from functions where a channel number is
1386:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         returned from ADC registers,
