2487:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   ADC trigger frequency mode must be set to low frequency when
2488:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         a duration is exceeded before ADC conversion start trigger event
