3491:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Get ADC group regular sequence: channel on rank corresponding to
3492:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         channel number.
3493:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   This function performs:
3494:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Channels order reading into each rank of scan sequence:
3495:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           rank of each channel is fixed by channel HW number
3496:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           (channel 0 fixed on rank 0, channel 1 fixed on rank1, ...).
3497:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, ADC group regular sequencer both modes
3498:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         "fully configurable" or "not fully configurable"
3499:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         are available, they can be chosen using
3500:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         function @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerConfigurable().
3501:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         This function can be used with setting "not fully configurable".
3502:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to description of functions @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerConfigurable()
3503:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         and @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerLength().
3504:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Depending on devices and packages, some channels may not be available.
3505:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to device datasheet for channels availability.
3506:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, to measure internal channels (VrefInt,
3507:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         TempSensor, ...), measurement paths to internal channels must be
3508:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         enabled separately.
