4519:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
4520:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Enable ADC instance internal voltage regulator.
4521:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, there are three possibilities to enable
4522:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         the voltage regulator:
4523:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - by enabling it manually
4524:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           using function @ref LL_ADC_EnableInternalRegulator().
4525:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - by launching a calibration
4526:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           using function @ref LL_ADC_StartCalibration().
4527:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - by enabling the ADC
4528:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           using function @ref LL_ADC_Enable().
4529:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, after ADC internal voltage regulator enable,
4530:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         a delay for ADC internal voltage regulator stabilization
4531:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         is required before performing a ADC calibration or ADC enable.
4532:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to device datasheet, parameter "tADCVREG_STUP".
4533:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to literal @ref LL_ADC_DELAY_INTERNAL_REGUL_STAB_US.
4534:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
4535:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
4536:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be ADC disabled.
4537:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CR       ADVREGEN       LL_ADC_EnableInternalRegulator
4538:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  ADCx ADC instance
4539:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @retval None
4540:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   */
4541:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h **** __STATIC_INLINE void LL_ADC_EnableInternalRegulator(ADC_TypeDef *ADCx)
4542:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h **** {
4543:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   /* Note: Write register with some additional bits forced to state reset     */
