4648:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Start ADC calibration in the mode single-ended
4649:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         or differential (for devices with differential mode available).
4650:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, a minimum number of ADC clock cycles
4651:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         are required between ADC end of calibration and ADC enable.
4652:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to literal @ref LL_ADC_DELAY_CALIB_ENABLE_ADC_CYCLES.
4653:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   In case of usage of ADC with DMA transfer:
4654:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         On this STM32 series, ADC DMA transfer request should be disabled
4655:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         during calibration:
4656:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Calibration factor is available in data register
4657:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         and also transferred by DMA.
4658:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         To not insert ADC calibration factor among ADC conversion data
4659:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         in array variable, DMA transfer must be disabled during
4660:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         calibration.
4661:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (DMA transfer setting backup and disable before calibration,
4662:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         DMA transfer setting restore after calibration.
4663:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to functions @ref LL_ADC_REG_GetDMATransfer(),
4664:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetDMATransfer() ).
4665:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   In case of usage of feature auto power-off:
